sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant AdminSystem
    participant Menu
    participant MenuManager
    participant Kiosk1 as Kiosk 1
    participant KioskN as Kiosk n

    Note over AdminSystem,KioskN: Observer pattern keeps all kiosk menus synchronised.
    Kiosk1->>AdminSystem: attach(this)
    KioskN->>AdminSystem: attach(this)
    Admin->>AdminSystem: updateAvailability(productId, false)
    AdminSystem->>Menu: findById(productId)
    Menu-->>AdminSystem: Product
    AdminSystem->>Menu: setAvailable(false)
    AdminSystem->>MenuManager: updateMenu(menu)
    MenuManager->>Kiosk1: update(menu)
    MenuManager->>KioskN: update(menu)
    AdminSystem->>Kiosk1: notifyObservers()
    AdminSystem->>KioskN: notifyObservers()
